nt||cp|8|AT|^B@2
hondo717: |cp||at|So I think 3@H is slightly better than 3@D as kia's bid. And, if moe leads anything but a club, it is down 1, so despite ira's 15 HCP plus 2 distribution points, it is not a great game.  moe's lead of a club is best from his hand. I would have led a club also. Unfortunately it doesn't work out. The reason a club is best in general (although not on this hand) is because leading an ace or away from an ace is usually not a good idea, as I have said many times. And leading a singleton trump, often gives away a trick. So, I think a club is the best lead, given the auction and what moe has even though it didn't happen to work on this hand.|
